Feasting at home with some Thai Cuisine from one of my fav Thai Restaurant @thanyingrestaurants located @arasingapore They are available for takeaway and islandwide wide delivery now!
.
These Thanying Set Specials inclusive of dessert of the day are priced at $16.00 nett. Ala Carte Menu is also available.
.
Visit https://www.thanyingrestaurants.com/home for more info
.
